The benchmark measures SAE performance across eight diverse metrics, spanning interpretability, feature disentanglement and practical applications like unlearning, with over 200 SAEs open-sourced across seven recently proposed SAE architectures and training algorithms.

**Key Findings:**

While Matryoshka SAEs slightly underperform on existing proxy metrics, they substantially outperform other architectures on feature disentanglement metrics, with this advantage growing with SAE scale.

